category="union"
<feature
<extension
<formats>
<spirvextensions
<spirvcapabilities

нужно расширить ktl::api::object_type и ktl::api::structure_type значениями из extension

## OPAQUE objects
```cpp
namespace
{
    struct opaque_instance final
    {
        using parent = void;
    };

    struct opaque_device final
    {
        using parent = opaque_instance;
    }
    struct opaque_phisical_device;
}

namespace ktl::api
{
    using ptr_instance = opaque_instance *;
    using ptr_device = opaque_device *;
    using ptr_phisical_device = opaque_phisical_device *;
}
```

## PNF
```cpp
namespace ktl::api
{
    using pnf_create_instance = ktl::api::result (*)(const vk_instance_create_info *, const allocator_callbacks *,
                                                    opaque_instance **);
}
```
